    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. Validation error (8.3% mean NIH) is within the 15% acceptance criterion. Mesh independence confirmed at GCI 1.9%. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 at the worst-case operating condition supports the device submission claim. Credibility evidence is sufficient to support regulatory use of CFD results for CPB hemolysis assessment at Class II device risk level.",
